om/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/charli-xcx-lorde@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/charli-xcx-lorde@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>已确认“Girl, so fusion”混音版是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lorde">Lorde</a>的想法 - 看看下面是如何产生的。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong><strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">Charli XCX – “Brat”评论：流行先锋完全拥抱舞池</a></strong></li></ul><p>Lorde 歌手最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-charli-xcxs-new-version-of-girl-so-confusing-with-lorde-3767515">参与了《Girl, so fusion》的混音版</a>，该歌曲最初出现在 Charli XCX 的最新专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">Brat</a> 》中。 Charli <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-admits-being-super-jealous-of-lordes-royals-success-3757196">之前曾谈到 Lorde 如何为这首歌曲提供部分灵感</a>，包括对她在“Royals”的成功感到嫉妒。</p><p> 《Brat》发行几周后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-charli-xcxs-new-version-of-girl-so-confusing-with-lorde-3767515">Charli 推出了该曲目的新版本，这次的主题是：Lorde</a> 。然而现在，查莉向<a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/pop/charli-xcx-brat-billboard-cover-story-interview-1235732025/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>公告牌</em></a>透露，混音完全是洛德的主意。 </p><figure id="attachment_3767520" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3767520" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3767520" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/charli_xcx_lorde.jpg" alt="Charli XCX 和洛德" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/charli_xcx_lorde.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/charli_xcx_lorde-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/charli_xcx_lorde-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/charli_xcx_lorde-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/charli_xcx_lorde-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/charli_xcx_lorde-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3767520" class="wp-caption-text"> Charli XCX 和 Lorde 在 2014 年 MTV 音乐录影带颁奖典礼上。 （MTV/MTV1415/Getty Images for MTV 拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>她解释说：“我必须先告诉她这首歌是关于她的，并且她对此表示同意。近一年来我一直想与她见面，但我们一直有这种奇怪的情况，就像我们本来[要去]，但后来又不去了。它讲述了歌曲本身的叙述。最终没有成功。”</p><p>查理继续说道：“然后在唱片发行的前一天，我给她留了一张语音留言。 [洛德]立即回答说，‘哦，天哪，我不知道你有这种感觉。我很抱歉。&#39;然后就像，“你知道，也许我应该出现在这首歌的一个版本中。”我什至没有问她。她提出来了。”</p><p> “这次推出的大部分内容都是计划好的，但有时却没有，”她总结道。 “Lorde 的混音版《Girl, so令人困惑》就是一个完美的例子。那不是计划好的。一共花了三天时间。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Charli xcx - 女孩，与 lorde 的版本令人困惑（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0q3K6FPzY18?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <i>NME</i><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">在对《Brat》的四星评论中</a>写道：“在<a href="https://x.com/charli_xcx/status/1761429574490194253">自称的‘俱乐部记录’</a>中，XCX 提供了纯粹的派对女孩享乐主义。渗透的节拍、急躁的合成器、左场制作和在顽皮的俏皮话或诚实的俏皮话之间穿梭的声线。”</p><p> “通过《Brat》，XCX 证明了走自己的路听起来总是不错，”它补充道。</p><p>六月发布后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lorde-praises-charli-xcxs-new-album-brat-there-is-no-one-like-this-bitch-3763486">洛德表达了她对《Brat》和查莉作为艺术家的钦佩</a>：“当我说被她的作品感动、改变和堵嘴是一种荣幸时，我代表我们所有人。没有人能像这个婊子一样。太棒了，欢迎小子。”</p><p>与此同时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lorde-is-teasing-her-fourth-album-online-3762772">洛德正在预告她的第四张专辑</a>。在她的 Instagram 更新中，她写道：“如果这些工具不存在，那么你在精神上有义务创造它们”，以及“L4”一词的变体。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-reveals-girl-so-confusing-remix-was-lordes-idea-3775918">Charli XCX 的帖子揭示了“Girl, so fusion”混音是 Lorde 的想法，该想法</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
唐纳德·格洛弗 (Donald Glover) 解释了他为何要停用幼稚的甘比诺 (Childish Gambino) 绰号https://www.nme.com/news/music/donald-glover-explains-why-hes-retiring-the-childish-gambino-moniker-3775910?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=donald-glover-explains-why-他让这个幼稚的甘比诺绰号退休了Surej SinghThu, 18 Jul 2024 02:57:49 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3775910 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Donald-Glover.-Credit_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="唐纳德·格洛弗。图片来源：Kevin Winter/Getty Images for iHeartMedia" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Donald-Glover.-Credit_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Donald-Glover.-Credit_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Donald-Glover.-Credit_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Donald-Glover.-Credit_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Donald-Glover.-Credit_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Donald-Glover.-Credit_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位说唱歌手将于本周发行他的最后一张幼稚甘比诺专辑</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/donald-glover-explains-why-hes-retiring-the-childish-gambino-moniker-3775910">唐纳德·格洛弗 (Donald Glover) 的帖子解释了他为何要退役“幼稚的甘比诺”(Childish Gambino) 绰号，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Donald-Glover.-Credit_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="唐纳德·格洛弗。图片来源：Kevin Winter/Getty Images for iHeartMedia" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Donald-Glover.-Credit_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Donald-Glover.-Credit_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Donald-Glover.-Credit_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Donald-Glover.-Credit_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Donald-Glover.-Credit_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Donald-Glover.-Credit_-Kevin-Winter_Getty-Images-for-iHeartMedia-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/donald-glover">唐纳德·格洛弗 (Donald Glover)</a>分享了他选择废除<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/childish-gambino">“幼稚甘比诺”(Childish Gambino)</a>绰号的原因 - 看看这位说唱歌手在下面怎么说。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/donald-glover-presents-what-did-it-mean-2626537">幼稚的甘比诺 - &#39;3.15.20&#39;评论：说唱界的文艺复兴人以迄今为止最多的个人记录放松警惕</a></strong></li></ul><p>明天（7 月 19 日），他将发行《Bando Stone &amp; The New World》，他说这将是“Childish Gambino”这个绰号的最后一张专辑。<a href="https://www.childishgambino.com/">现在可以预保存</a>相册了。</p><p> 《Bando Stone &amp; The New World》专辑还将作为同名新电影的官方配乐。唐纳德·格洛弗最近<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V44EenldJQs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">透露了这部电影的预告片</a>，尽管该电影尚未确定上映日期。</p><p>这位演员、说唱歌手、喜剧演员兼作家在接受<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2024/07/17/arts/music/donald-glover-childish-gambino-bando-stone.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>采访时谈到了与甘比诺的告别。在录制这张专辑时，格洛弗意识到：“这真的就像是，‘哦，完成了。’”这并不令人满意。我只是觉得我不再需要以这种方式建造了。”</p><p>但这并不是唯一的原因。他分享说，在制作这张专辑和<em>《Bando Stone》</em>电影时，他面临着几个问题，即他应该将精力投入到生活的哪些领域。在父亲去世和几个孩子出生后，格洛弗现在除了演艺事业和制作公司 Gilga 之外，还想专注于家庭。 </p><figure id="attachment_3755582" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3755582" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3755582" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/childish-gambino@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/childish-gambino@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/childish-gambino@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/childish-gambino@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/childish-gambino@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/childish-gambino@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/childish-gambino@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3755582" class="wp-caption-text">唐纳德·格洛弗 (Donald Glover) 又名幼稚甘比诺 (Childish Gambino) 在 2024 年 Met Gala 上。图片来源：Marleen Moise/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>他还告诉《<em>纽约时报》</em> ，包括“专辑消费持续下降”和“巡演业务中断”在内的其他因素也影响了他让幼稚甘比诺退休的决定。他也不再对追逐排行榜上的成功感兴趣。</p><p> <strong class="css-8qgvsz ebyp5n10">“</strong>老实说，对我来说成功就是能够推出一张我愿意听的大型专辑，”他说。 “对于这张专辑，我真的希望能够在大房间里演奏，并在这些房间里充满宏大的国歌歌曲，这样人们就会有一种团结的感觉。”</p><p>最近，格洛弗<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/childish-gambino-drops-new-single-in-the-night-ft-jorja-smith-and-amaarae-3775388">本周早些时候</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jorja-smith">乔贾·史密斯</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amaarae">阿玛拉</a>分享了一首名为“In The Night”的新单曲。这是“Bando Stone”专辑中的第二首歌曲， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/donald-glover-shares-new-single-sets-date-for-final-album-3771562">紧随本月早些时候发行的“Lithonia”之后</a>。</p><p>五月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/childish-gambino-drops-atavista-album-and-music-video-for-little-foot-big-foot-3755581">格洛弗发行了他的最新专辑“Atavista</a> ”。他在社交媒体上宣布发行这张专辑，这是他的 2020 年唱片《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/donald-glover-presents-what-did-it-mean-2626537">3.15.20</a> 》的“完整”版本。这张专辑现已在流媒体上推出，音乐家重新创作了 2020 年唱片中的曲目，并添加了一首新歌“Little Foot Big Foot”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/donald-glover-presents-what-did-it-mean-2626537">《2020 年 3 月 15 日》在 2020 年首次发行时被<em>NME</em>评为四星</a>：“格洛弗愿意分享记录在案的如此坦诚的时刻，这特别有趣，因为他过去倾向于将自己的私生活基本上保持在离线状态，这可能是这表明，随着外界继续试图窥探，这位明星开始放松警惕。 </p><figure id="attachment_3431067" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3431067" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3431067" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_donaldglover_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="唐纳德·格洛弗" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_donaldglover_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_donaldglover_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_donaldglover_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_donaldglover_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_donaldglover_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/2023_donaldglover_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3431067" class="wp-caption-text">唐纳德·格洛弗 (Donald Glover) 于 2023 年 3 月 5 日出席在纽约市爱迪生宴会厅举行的第 75 届作家协会颁奖典礼 图片来源：Jamie McCarthy/Getty Images for Writers Guild of America East</figcaption></figure><p> “格洛弗至少在他的音乐作品中运用了这种方法，令人印象深刻的《3.15.20》非常值得等待——那么，我们会祈祷他不会屈服于过去的闪烁其辞然后再把记录记下来……”</p><p>其他消息方面，Childish Gambino 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/childish-gambinos-new-world-tour-dates-venues-and-ticket-details-revealed-for-uk-europe-and-australia-3755849">确认了他的“新世界”巡演的日期和地点</a>，巡演将于今年晚些时候到 2025 年在英国、欧洲和澳大利亚进行。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/childish-gambinos-new-world-tour-dates-venues-and-ticket-details-revealed-for-uk-europe-and-australia-3755849">请在此处查看完整的巡演日期列表，</a>并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fchildish-gambino-tickets%2Fartist%2F1503424" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处</a>购买门票。 </p><figure id="attachment_3563966" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3563966" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3563966" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/childish-gambino-new-music-soon.jpg" alt="唐纳德·格洛弗" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/childish-gambino-new-music-soon.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/childish-gambino-new-music-soon-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/childish-gambino-new-music-soon-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/childish-gambino-new-music-soon-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/childish-gambino-new-music-soon-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/childish-gambino-new-music-soon-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3563966" class="wp-caption-text">唐纳德·格洛弗 (Donald Glover) 于 2023 年 4 月 6 日在纽约出席《GQ》全球创意奖（图片来源：Theo Wargo/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>最近，格洛弗<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/donald-glover-shades-bet-i-have-the-same-amount-of-bet-awards-as-sam-smith-3771006">称赞黑人娱乐电视奖（BET）</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-smith">萨姆·史密斯的</a>奖项数量相同。 “这不是针对我个人的，但我只是觉得我应该获得更多 BET 奖项，”他开始说道。 “我是认真的。这是黑人娱乐电视奖。我还需要做多少有趣的事情？因为这只是事实的数学计算。”</p><p> “这确实没有意义，”这位博学者补充道。 “我获得的格莱美奖比威尔·史密斯多，这毫无意义，但我和萨姆·史密斯获得的 BET 奖项数量相同。这对你们来说有意义吗？我和萨姆·史密斯在黑人娱乐电视[奖项]上并驾齐驱”。格洛弗凭借《This Is America》荣获 2019 年最佳音乐录影带奖，而史密斯则荣获 2015 年最佳新人奖。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/donald-glover-explains-why-hes-retiring-the-childish-gambino-moniker-3775910">唐纳德·格洛弗 (Donald Glover) 的帖子解释了他为何要退役“幼稚的甘比诺”(Childish Gambino) 绰号，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
史蒂文·威尔逊 (Steven Wilson) 表示他从未称酷玩乐队为“混蛋” https://www.nme.com/news/music/steven-wilson-says-he-never-known-coldplay-wankers-3775896?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=steven-wilson-says-he-never-known-酷玩乐队Laura MolloyWed, 17 Jul 2024 20:42:58 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronicRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3775896 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steven-Wilson.-Credit_-Guy-Prives_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="史蒂文·威尔逊.图片来源：Guy Prives/Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steven-Wilson.-Credit_-Guy-Prives_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steven-Wilson.-Credit_-Guy-Prives_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steven-Wilson.-Credit_-Guy-Prives_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steven-Wilson.-Credit_-Guy-Prives_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steven-Wilson.-Credit_-Guy-Prives_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steven-Wilson.-Credit_-Guy-Prives_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “直到今天，我仍然在采访中被问及我对酷玩乐队的传奇般的仇恨”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/steven-wilson-says-he-never-called-coldplay-wankers-3775896">史蒂文·威尔逊 (Steven Wilson) 表示他从未称酷玩乐队为“混蛋”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steven-Wilson.-Credit_-Guy-Prives_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="史蒂文·威尔逊.图片来源：Guy Prives/Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steven-Wilson.-Credit_-Guy-Prives_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steven-Wilson.-Credit_-Guy-Prives_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steven-Wilson.-Credit_-Guy-Prives_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steven-Wilson.-Credit_-Guy-Prives_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steven-Wilson.-Credit_-Guy-Prives_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Steven-Wilson.-Credit_-Guy-Prives_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/steven-wilson">史蒂文·威尔逊 (Steven Wilson)</a>打破了近两年来他称<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">酷玩乐队</a>为“混蛋”的神话。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/steven-wilson-interview-harmony-codex-economies-scale-manic-street-preachers-porcupine-tree-3490247">史蒂文·威尔逊谈新专辑《The Harmony Codex》：“我很荣幸能做我想做的事”</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天（7 月 17 日），这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/porcupine-tree">豪猪树</a>歌手兼多乐器演奏家终于解决了他举着“酷玩乐队都是混蛋”标语的臭名昭著的形象。这张照片拍摄于 2006 年美国的 Porcupine Tree 演出，在网上疯传，多年来粉丝们都将其视为威尔逊对酷玩乐队立场的官方确认。</p><p>现在，威尔逊在 Instagram 上一劳永逸地澄清了谣言，承认他当时实际上是酷玩乐队的粉丝，并且今天仍然继续听他们的音乐。</p><p>威尔逊分享说，这个牌子是一位观众递给他的，他写道：“现在我有点喜欢酷玩乐队（现在仍然喜欢），所以我很困惑，举起牌子问作者一些类似于为什么他们写了这样一个不正确和不恰当的声明。”</p><p>他继续说道：“对我来说不幸的是，有人在我举起标语的那一刻给我拍了一张照片，这张照片被上传到互联网上并迅速传播开来，每个人都将其中所写的情感归因于我。”</p><p>威尔逊表示，尽管这张照片是 18 年前拍摄的，但它留下的痕迹却一直困扰着他多年。 “直到今天，我仍然在采访中被问及我对酷玩乐队的传奇般的仇恨，”他写道。</p><p>但事实证明，他仍然是他的粉丝。他鼓励任何仍存疑虑的粉丝去看看 Coldplay 2021 年专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/coldplay-music-of-the-spheres-review-3070711">Music Of The Spheres</a> 》中的“极其精彩”的歌曲《Coloratura》，并写道：“你稍后可以感谢我……” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9h5jyvsfe8/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; m